  "subject": "Fix missing request header exception",
  "commit_message": "Fix missing request header exception\n\nWhat’s happening is portal tries to authenticate to SDC fe,\nSDC checks cookies for userId, but userId remains empty as\nassignment from the decryption is no longer done to userId,\nhence SDC refuse the connection saying missing header…\n\nChange-Id: If9f5ca9749616624a1ecd3a6926eaf2f0ebe431e\nIssue-ID: SDC-1839\nSigned-off-by: Alexis de Talhouët <adetalhouet89@gmail.com>\n",
